column10: Jagna is a young woman determined to forge her own path in a late 19th century Polish village - a hotbed of gossip and on-going feuds, held together, rich and poor, by adherence to colorful traditions and deep-rooted patriarchy.

column9: Tom Rhys Harries, Farhad Bagheri, Gerard Butler
column10: A CIA operative and his translator flee from special forces in Afghanistan after exposing a covert mission.
